snippet.title: Nerd³ Makes... How To Snooker
snippet.description:
I suppose I'm officially a game dev now! Woo!

Game Link: http://www.nerdcubed.co.uk/games/

End theme by the incredible Dan Bull: 
http://www.youtube.com/user/douglby

All other music is in game music. It makes me want to build more games!

http://nerdcubed.co.uk/
